OL,3,CMemorial service held on the 37th
OL,4,Canniversary of the Lockerbie Pan Am
OL,5,Cbombing
OL,7,FA remembrance service was held on
OL,8,FSunday December 21 to mark the 37th
OL,9,Fanniversary of the Pan Am bombing in
OL,10,FLockerbie.
OL,12,FAll of the passengers and crew on
OL,13,Fboard Pan Am Flight 103 - 270 people -
OL,14,Fwere killed when the plane exploded
OL,15,Fover Lockerbie on 21st December 1988
OL,16,Fin a terrorist attack.
