OL,5,Cbombing
OL,7,FThe service was the first was to be
OL,8,Fheld at the Lockerbie Memorial Church
OL,9,FMuseum, which was formerly the
OL,10,FDryfesdale & Trinity Church building.
OL,11,FThe Pan Am 103 Lockerbie Legacy
OL,12,FFoundation bought the building this
OL,13,Fyear, and it is now undergoing
OL,14,Frestoration.
OL,16,FHis Majesty's Lord Lieutenant of
OL,17,FDumfries, Fiona Armstrong, spoke at
OL,18,Fthe service.
