OL,7,FShe said: "37 years on, it is a time
OL,8,Fof deep reflection. A time to remember
OL,9,Fthose who died and a time to pay
OL,10,Ftribute
OL,12,Fto those who helped this Dumfriesshire
OL,13,Fcommunity in the days, weeks and years
OL,14,Fthat followed."
OL,16,FLord Lieutenant Armstrong also paid
OL,17,Ftribute to those involved at the scene.
