OL,7,FShe offered thanks to: "Friends and
OL,8,Ffamily of those who died here 37 years
OL,9,Fago. Police, fire, ambulance, mountain
OL,10,Frescue.
OL,12,F"Those who baked to feed emergency
OL,13,Fservices, those who washed the clothes
OL,14,Fof victims to send them back to their
OL,15,Floved ones. Those who coped, those who
OL,16,Fhelped, those who cared."
