OL,4,Canniversary of the Lockerbie Pan Am
OL,5,Cbombing
OL,7,FLinny Oliphant lives in Lockerbie, and
OL,8,Fwas a school girl at the time of the
OL,9,Fbombing. She is now the UK Executive
OL,10,FDirector of the Pan Am 103 Lockerbie
OL,11,FLegacy Foundation.
OL,13,FAt the service she said: "We honour
OL,14,Fthe 270 innocent killed in the air and
OL,15,Fon the ground. We pay gratitude to the
OL,16,Famazing response of over 110
OL,17,Forganisations to the scene in
OL,18,FLockerbie, and we honour the town's
OL,19,Fpeople.
