OL,7,F"We would like to express our deepest
OL,8,Fgratitude for joining us here today in
OL,9,Fremembrance."
OL,11,FIts CEO, Victoria Cummock, said: "I am
OL,12,Fhonoured to lead the charge of
OL,13,FLocardians and many supporters to
OL,14,Frescue and reopen the doors of this
OL,15,Ficonic site.
