OL,5,Cbombing
OL,7,F"Together, we will resume the
OL,8,Ftradition, which began in 1989 within
OL,9,FDryfesdale Church, to build a lasting
OL,10,Flegacy of commemoration and education
OL,11,Fabout Lockerbie, the town that taught
OL,12,Fthe world a lesson in humanity."
OL,14,FThe service also featured a 'Wall of
OL,15,FHonour' coat of arms display, which
OL,16,Fpays tribute to the the responder
OL,17,Forganisations that dealt with the
OL,18,Faftermath of the disaster.
